text: Edinah Rotich (born 27 March 1981) is a Kenyan volleyball player. She is part of the Kenyan women's national volleyball team. She competed at the 2007 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup, and 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for Kenya Commercial Bank and Friends Volleyball Club. == References == Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan volleyball players
